divs: Sighting DetailsI was just going on a bike ride. i rode to this place specifically to take some pictures and admire the view. it was clear sky and there were no birds and no ufo's as far as i knew. later i got home and uploaded one of my pictures to instagram and noticed there was a black object in the sky so i had a look at the other 2 photos i had taken and there were 9 black objects in both photos in different positions from one photo to the other and i took these pictures over a period of 5 minutes. I have had close to 40 sightings of individual ufos in my life from zig zagging stars to Green fluorecent Orbs, Burning orange balls, cloaked things in the sky and the list goes on. I am beggining to think that i'm being contacted because i barely know anyone who has seen one unless they have been with me. to see this many is just unheard of. i have a picture of a burning orange ball too.
